<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Many companies=C2=A0do at least a=C2=A0<em>lit=
tle=C2=A0</em>bit of earnings management and =E2=80=9Cwindow dressing.=E2=
=80=9D If it is getting to be mid-to-late December and there is a sale that=
 you have <em>almost=C2=A0</em>closed, or an expense that you=E2=80=99ll pr=
obably have to pay pretty soon, you will sit down and say =E2=80=9Cwell, ou=
r year is almost over, do we want this sale (or expense) to count for this =
year, or next year?=E2=80=9D The answer will depend on your particular situ=
ation, but often you will=C2=A0want to book revenue early and expenses late=
: You=E2=80=99ll rush to close the sale in December, and foot-drag on payin=
g the expense until January, so that you can report higher income for this =
fiscal year. You want this year to look as good as possible; you=E2=80=99ll=
 worry about next year later.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As an official matter, the US Securities and E=
xchange Commission frowns upon this sort of thing; there are <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32912729.260424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
c2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzLzIwMTAvMjAxMC0xNjkuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3=
0d097a7" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" s=
tyle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wid=
th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;"> rules</a> and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/32912729.260424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9lbmZvcmNlLzMzLTExM=
Dk2LXM/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB1f4d75be" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> enforcement actions</a>=
. But the SEC=E2=80=99s fiscal year ends on Sept. 30 and, let me tell you, =
there sure were a lot of high-dollar enforcement actions last week. =E2=80=
=9CWall Street=E2=80=99s top regulator on Friday brought in $218 million in=
 fines, roughly equal to 10% of its latest annual budget,=E2=80=9D <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32912729.260424/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9maW5hbmNlL3JlZ3VsYXRpb24vc2Vjcy13aGF0c2FwcC1maW5lcy1zcHJl=
YWQtZnVydGhlci1hY3Jvc3Mtd2FsbC1zdHJlZXQtZjFmMDk3ZWE_bW9kPWl0cF93c2o/607f07c=
eef4b8524a319a23cB48809585" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" =
target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important=
; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> counts the Wall Street Journal</a>. I =
count <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32912729.260=
424/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9uZXdzL3ByZXNzcmVsZWFzZXM/607f07ceef4b8524a31=
9a23cB8d872e57" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_b=
lank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bot=
tom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; b=
ackground-color: #ccc;"> seven enforcement actions</a>, against 16 firms, j=
ust on Friday, plus five more on Thursday.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=
=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inli=
ne-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Could any of those cases have waited until Monday? Well. Now is a=
 different fiscal year!=C2=A0You want to meet your earnings expectations.</=
p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I am kidding, I think? I am not really sure.=
=C2=A0Anyway lots of cases; let=E2=80=99s go through some of them quickly.<=
/p>
